[section#exec.task.scheduler
    [`execution::task_scheduler]
]

[codeblock:synopsis]
namespace std::execution {
  class [[redoc("`:lib>")]]task_scheduler {
    class [[redoc("*>")]]ts-domain;                      // [=expos]

    template<[[redoc("`:c>")]]scheduler Sch>
      class [[redoc("*>")]]backend-for;                  // [=expos]

  public:
    using scheduler_concept = scheduler_tag;

    template<class Sch, class Allocator = allocator<void>>
      requires (![[redoc("`:c>")]]same_as<task_scheduler, remove_cvref_t<Sch>>) && [[redoc("`:c>")]]scheduler<Sch>
    explicit task_scheduler(Sch&& sch, Allocator alloc = {});

    task_scheduler(const task_scheduler&) = default;
    task_scheduler& operator=(const task_scheduler&) = default;

    [[redoc("[=seebelow]")]] schedule();

    friend bool operator==(const task_scheduler& lhs, const task_scheduler& rhs) noexcept;
    template<class Sch>
      requires (![[redoc("`:c>")]]same_as<task_scheduler, Sch>) && [[redoc("`:c>")]]scheduler<Sch>
    friend bool operator==(const task_scheduler& lhs, const Sch& rhs) noexcept;

  private:
    // [:en] see [#exec.parschedrepl.psb] [:zh_CN] 见 [#exec.parschedrepl.psb]
    shared_ptr<parallel_scheduler_replacement::parallel_scheduler_backend> [[redoc("*>")]]sch_;  // [=expos]
  };
}
[codeblock:end]

[para]
[:en] [`task_scheduler] is a class that models [`:c scheduler] ([#exec.sched]).
[:zh_CN] [`task_scheduler] 是构成 [`:c scheduler] 类（[#exec.sched]）。

[:en] Given an object [`s] of type [`task_scheduler], let [`[*SCHED](s)] be the
object pointed to by the pointer owned by [`s.[*sch_]].
[:zh_CN] 给定 [`task_scheduler] 类型的对象 [`s]，令 [`[*SCHED](s)] 为
[`s.[*sch_]] 所拥有的指针指向的对象。

[:en] The expression [`get_forward_progress_guarantee(s)] is equivalent to
[`get_forward_progress_guarantee([*SCHED](s))].
[:zh_CN] 表达式 [`get_forward_progress_guarantee(s)] 等价于
[`get_forward_progress_guarantee([*SCHED](s))]。

[:en] The expression [`get_completion_domain<set_value_t>(s)] is equivalent to
[`task_scheduler::[*ts-domain]()].
[:zh_CN] 表达式 [`get_completion_domain<set_value_t>(s)] 等价于
[`task_scheduler::[*ts-domain]()]。

[%@lib@ctor task_scheduler]
[codeblock:declaration]
template<class Sch, class Allocator = allocator<void>>
  requires(![[redoc("`:c>")]]same_as<task_scheduler, remove_cvref_t<Sch>>) && [[redoc("`:c>")]]scheduler<Sch>
explicit task_scheduler(Sch&& sch, Allocator alloc = {});
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:mandates]
[:en] [`Sch] satisfies [`[*:c infallible-scheduler]<env<>>].
[:zh_CN] [`Sch] 满足 [`[*:c infallible-scheduler]<env<>>]。

[para:effects]
[:en] Initializes [*sch_] with:
[:zh_CN] 使用以下内容初始化 [*sch_]：
[codeblock]
allocate_shared<[[redoc("*>")]]backend-for<remove_cvref_t<Sch>>>(alloc, std::forward<Sch>(sch))
[codeblock:end]

[para:recommended]
[:en] Implementations should avoid the use of dynamically
allocated memory for small scheduler objects.
[:zh_CN] 实现应避免为小型调度器对象使用动态分配的内存。

[para:remarks]
[:en] Any allocations performed by calls on [`*this] are performed using a copy of [`alloc].
[:zh_CN] [`*this] 上的调用执行的任何分配都使用 [`alloc] 的副本执行。
[div:end]

[%@lib@member operator==[!task_scheduler]]
[codeblock:declaration]
bool operator==(const task_scheduler& lhs, const task_scheduler& rhs) noexcept;
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] Equivalent to: [`return lhs == [*SCHED](rhs);]
[:zh_CN] 等价于：[`return lhs == [*SCHED](rhs);]
[div:end]

[%@lib@member operator==[!task_scheduler]]
[codeblock:declaration]
template<class Sch>
  requires (![[redoc("`:c>")]]same_as<task_scheduler, Sch>)
        && [[redoc("`:c>")]]scheduler<Sch>
bool operator==(const task_scheduler& lhs, const Sch& rhs) noexcept;
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:returns]
[:en] [`false] if type of [`[*SCHED](lhs)] is not [`Sch], otherwise [`[*SCHED](lhs) == rhs].
[:zh_CN] 如果 [`[*SCHED](lhs)] 的类型并非 [`Sch] 则返回 [`false]，否则返回 [`[*SCHED](lhs) == rhs]。
[div:end]

[para]
[:en] For an lvalue [`r] of a type derived from [`receiver_proxy],
let [`[*WRAP-RCVR](r)] be an object of a type that models [`:c receiver] and whose
completion handlers result in invoking the corresponding completion handlers of [`r].
[:zh_CN] 对于 [`receiver_proxy] 派生类型的左值 [`r]，令 [`[*WRAP-RCVR](r)] 为一个
构成 [`:c receiver] 的类型的对象，并且其完成处理器会导致调用 [`r] 的相应完成处理器。

[codeblock:synopsis]
namespace std::execution {
  template<[[redoc("`:c>")]]scheduler Sch>
  class task_scheduler::[[redoc("*>")]]backend-for
    : public parallel_scheduler_replacement::parallel_scheduler_backend {       // [=expos]
  public:
    explicit [[redoc("*>")]]backend-for(Sch sch) : [[redoc("*>")]]sched_(std::move(sch)) {}

    void schedule(receiver_proxy& r, span<byte> s) noexcept override;
    void schedule_bulk_chunked(size_t shape, bulk_item_receiver_proxy& r,
                               span<byte> s) noexcept override;
    void schedule_bulk_unchunked(size_t shape, bulk_item_receiver_proxy& r,
                                 span<byte> s) noexcept override;

  private:
    Sch [[redoc("*>")]]sched_;
  };
}
[codeblock:end]

[para]
[:en] Let [`env] be a pack of subexpressions, and let [*just-sndr-like] be a sender
whose only value completion signature is [`set_value_t()] and for which the expression
[`get_completion_scheduler<set_value_t>(get_env([*just-sndr-like]), env...)]
is expression-equivalent to [`get_completion_scheduler<set_value_t>([*sched_], env...)].
[:zh_CN] 令 [`env] 是一个子表达式包，并且令 [*just-sndr-like] 是一个发送器，其唯一的
值完成签名为 [`set_value_t()]，并且表达式
[`get_completion_scheduler<set_value_t>(get_env([*just-sndr-like]), env...)]
按表达式等价于 [`get_completion_scheduler<set_value_t>([*sched_], env...)]。

[codeblock:declaration]
void schedule(receiver_proxy& r, span<byte> s) noexcept override;
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] Constructs an operation state [`os] with
[`connect(schedule([*sched_]), [*WRAP-RCVR](r))] and calls [`start(os)].
[:zh_CN] 构造一个操作状态 [`os]，使用 [`connect(schedule([*sched_]), [*WRAP-RCVR](r))]，并调用 [`start(os)]。
[div:end]

[codeblock:declaration]
void schedule_bulk_chunked(size_t shape, bulk_item_receiver_proxy& r,
                           span<byte> s) noexcept override;
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] Let [`chunk_size] be an integer less than or equal to [`shape],
let [`num_chunks] be [`(shape + chunk_size - 1) / chunk_size], and
let [`fn] be a function object such that for an integer [`i],
[`fn(i)] calls [`r.execute(i * chunk_size, m)],
where [`m] is the lesser of [`(i + 1) * chunk_size] and [`shape].
[:zh_CN] 令 [`chunk_size] 是一个小于或等于 [`shape] 的整数，令 [`num_chunks] 为
[`(shape + chunk_size - 1) / chunk_size]，并令 [`fn] 为一个函数对象，使得对于整数 [`i]，
[`fn(i)] 调用 [`r.execute(i * chunk_size, m)]，其中 [`m] 是 [`(i + 1) * chunk_size] 和
[`shape] 中较小的那个。

[:en] Constructs an operation state [`os] as if with
[:zh_CN] 构造一个操作状态 [`os]，如同使用以下内容：
[codeblock]
connect(bulk([[redoc("*>")]]just-sndr-like, par, num_chunks, fn), [[redoc("*>")]]WRAP-RCVR(r))
[codeblock:end]
[:en@~] and calls [`start(os)].
[:zh_CN@~] 并调用 [`start(os)]。
[div:end]

[codeblock:declaration]
void schedule_bulk_unchunked(size_t shape, bulk_item_receiver_proxy& r,
                             span<byte> s) noexcept override;
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:effects]
[:en] Let [`fn] be a function object such that for an integer [`i],
[`fn(i)] is equivalent to [`r.execute(i, i + 1)].
[:zh_CN] 令 [`fn] 为一个函数对象，使得对于整数 [`i]，[`fn(i)] 等价于 [`r.execute(i, i + 1)]。

[:en] Constructs an operation state [`os] as if with
[:zh_CN] 构造一个操作状态 [`os]，如同使用以下内容：
[codeblock]
connect(bulk([[redoc("*>")]]just-sndr-like, par, shape, fn), [[redoc("*>")]]WRAP-RCVR(r))
[codeblock:end]
[:en@~] and calls [`start(os)].
[:zh_CN@~] 并调用 [`start(os)]。
[div:end]

[codeblock:declaration]
[[redoc("[=seebelow]")]] schedule();
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:returns]
[:en] A prvalue [*ts-sndr] whose type models [`:c sender] such that:
[:zh_CN] 一个纯右值 [*ts-sndr]，其类型构成 [`:c sender]，使得：

[list]
[item]
[:en] [`get_completion_scheduler<set_value_t>(get_env([*ts-sndr]))] is equal to [`*this].
[:zh_CN] [`get_completion_scheduler<set_value_t>(get_env([*ts-sndr]))] 等于 [`*this]。

[item]
[:en] [`get_completion_domain<set_value_t>(get_env([*ts-sndr]))]
is expression-equivalent to [`[*ts-domain]()].
[:zh_CN] [`get_completion_domain<set_value_t>(get_env([*ts-sndr]))] 按表达式等价于 [`[*ts-domain]()]。

[item]
[:en] If a receiver [`rcvr] is connected to [*ts-sndr] and
the resulting operation state is started, calls [`[*sch_]->schedule(r, s)], where
[:zh_CN] 如果接收器 [`rcvr] 已连接到 [*ts-sndr] 并且结果操作状态已启动，则调用
[`[*sch_]->schedule(r, s)]，其中
 [list]
 [item]
[:en@~] [`r] is a proxy for [`rcvr] with base
[`parallel_scheduler_replacement::receiver_proxy] ([#exec.par.scheduler]) and
[:zh_CN@~] [`r] 是一个针对 [`rcvr] 的以 [`parallel_scheduler_replacement::receiver_proxy]
为基类的代理（[#exec.par.scheduler]），以及
 [item]
[:en@~] [`s] is a preallocated backend storage for [`r].
[:zh_CN@~] [`s] 是为 [`r] 预分配的后端存储。
 [list:end]

[item]
[:en] For any type [`E], [`completion_signatures_of_t<decltype([*ts-sndr]), E>]
denotes [`completion_signatures<set_value_t()>] if
[`[`:c unstoppable_token]<stop_token_of_t<E>>] is [`true], and
otherwise [`completion_signatures<set_value_t(), set_stopped_t()>].
[:zh_CN] 对于任何类型 [`E]，如果 [`[`:c unstoppable_token]<stop_token_of_t<E>>] 是 [`true]，
则 [`completion_signatures_of_t<decltype([*ts-sndr]), E>] 表示
[`completion_signatures<set_value_t()>]，否则表示
[`completion_signatures<set_value_t(), set_stopped_t()>]。
[list:end]
[div:end]

[codeblock]
namespace std::execution {
  class task_scheduler::[[redoc("*>")]]ts-domain : public default_domain {     // [=expos]
  public:
    template<class BulkSndr, class Env>
      static constexpr auto transform_sender(set_value_t, BulkSndr&& bulk_sndr, const Env& env)
        noexcept([[redoc("[=seebelow]")]]);
  };
}
[codeblock:end]

[codeblock:declaration]
template<class BulkSndr, class Env>
  static constexpr auto transform_sender(BulkSndr&& bulk_sndr, const Env& env)
    noexcept(is_nothrow_constructible_v<decay_t<BulkSndr>, BulkSndr>);
[codeblock:end]

[div:description]
[para:constraints]
[list]
[item]
[:en] [`[`:c sender_in]<BulkSndr, Env>] is [`true],
[:zh_CN] [`[`:c sender_in]<BulkSndr, Env>] 为 [`true]，
[item]
[:en] [`auto(std::forward<BulkSndr>(bulk_sndr))] is well-formed, and
[:zh_CN] [`auto(std::forward<BulkSndr>(bulk_sndr))] 良构，并且
[item]
[:en] either
[:zh_CN] 或者
 [list]
 [item]
[:en@~] [`[*:c sender-for]<BulkSndr, bulk_chunked_t>] or
[:zh_CN@~] [`[*:c sender-for]<BulkSndr, bulk_chunked_t>] 或者
 [item]
[:@~] [`[*:c sender-for]<BulkSndr, bulk_unchunked_t>]
 [list:end]
[:en@~] is [`true].
[:zh_CN@~] 为 [`true]。
[list:end]

[para:effects]
[:en] Equivalent to:
[:zh_CN] 等价于：
[codeblock]
auto& [_, data, child] = bulk_sndr;
auto& [_, shape, fn] = data;
auto sch = [[redoc("*>")]]call-with-default(get_completion_scheduler<set_value_t>,
                             [[redoc("*>")]]not-a-scheduler(), get_env(child), [[redoc("*>")]]FWD-ENV(env));
return [[redoc("$>")]]e;
[codeblock:end]
[:en@~] where [$e] is [`[*not-a-sender]()] if the type of [`sch] is not [`task_scheduler];
otherwise, it is a prvalue whose type models [`:c sender] such that,
if it is connected to a receiver [`rcvr] and the resulting operation state is started,
[`child] is connected to an unspecified receiver [`R] and started.
[:zh_CN@~] 其中 [$e] 在 [`sch] 的类型不是 [`task_scheduler] 时为 [`[*not-a-sender]()]；
否则它是一个类型构成 [`:c sender] 的纯右值，使得如果它连接到一个接收器 [`rcvr] 并且
结果操作状态已启动，则 [`child] 连接到一个未指定的接收器 [`R] 并且已启动。

[para:~]
[:en] The expression [`get_env(R)] is expression-equivalent to
[`[*FWD-ENV](get_env([*rcvr-copy]))], where [*rcvr-copy] is an lvalue subexpression
designating an object decay-copied from [`rcvr].
[:zh_CN] 表达式 [`get_env(R)] 按表达式等价于 [`[*FWD-ENV](get_env([*rcvr-copy]))]，
其中 [*rcvr-copy] 是一个左值子表达式，指定一个从 [`rcvr] 退化复制的对象。

[para:~]
[:en] If [`child] completes with an error or a stopped completion,
the completion operation is forwarded unchanged to [`rcvr].
[:zh_CN] 如果 [`child] 以错误或停止完成，则完成操作不变地转发到 [`rcvr]。

[:en] Otherwise, let [`args] be a pack of lvalue subexpressions
designating objects decay-copied from the value result datums.
[:zh_CN] 否则，令 [`args] 是一个左值子表达式包，指定从值结果数据项退化复制的对象。

[:en] Then:
[:zh_CN] 然后：

[list]
[item]
[:en] If [`bulk_sndr] was the result of the evaluation of an expression
equivalent to [`bulk_chunked(child, policy, shape, fn)] or a copy of such,
then [`[*sch_]->schedule_bulk_chunked(shape, r, s)] is called
where [`r] is a bulk chunked proxy ([#exec.par.scheduler])
for [`rcvr] with callable [`fn] and arguments [`args], and
[`s] is a preallocated backend storage for [`r].
[:zh_CN] 如果 [`bulk_sndr] 是对一个等价于 [`bulk_chunked(child, policy, shape, fn)]
的表达式的求值结果或其副本，则调用 [`[*sch_]->schedule_bulk_chunked(shape, r, s)]，
其中 [`r] 是一个具有可调用体 [`fn] 和实参 [`args] 的针对 [`rcvr] 的批量分块代理（[#exec.par.scheduler]），
并且 [`s] 是为 [`r] 预分配的后端存储。

[item]
[:en] Otherwise, calls [`[*sch_]->schedule_bulk_unchunked(shape, r, s)]
where [`r] is a bulk unchunked proxy for [`rcvr] with callable [`fn] and
arguments [`args], and [`s] is a preallocated backend storage for [`r].
[:zh_CN] 否则，调用 [`[*sch_]->schedule_bulk_unchunked(shape, r, s)]，
其中 [`r] 是一个具有可调用体 [`fn] 和实参 [`args] 的针对 [`rcvr] 的批量非分块代理，
并且 [`s] 是为 [`r] 预分配的后端存储。
[list:end]
[div:end]
